    <title>长摘要-安全和效益可以兼得</title>
    <link>http://localhost:1313/research/%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E4%B8%8E%E6%95%88%E7%9B%8A%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E5%85%BC%E5%BE%97/</link>
